headline: Citizens Financial Services (CZFS) Tops Q4 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Citizens Financial Services (CZFS) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 9.09% and 0.05%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: Citizens Vice Chair and Chief Experience Officer Beth Johnson to Retire
summary: PROVIDENCE, R.I., January 30, 2025--Citizens Financial Group, Inc. (NYSE: CFG) today announced that Beth Johnson, Vice Chair and Chief Experience Officer, will retire from the bank, effective March 3. Johnson, a member of the bank’s Executive Committee, currently oversees a portfolio that includes customer experience and digital design, data & analytics, marketing & communications, enterprise payments strategy, and the bank’s sustainability & impact programs.
